  "workflow_summary": "Real-time operator cockpit over a local filesystem project, facilitating AI CLI execution with an interactive authorization boundary (human-in-the-loop). The system creates claude subprocess sessions, relays structured JSON streams over WebSocket to a React/Zustand frontend, and bridges tool_use permission events back to the operator.",
